{"tid":2128640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支共︰紐西蘭暫停與香港引渡協議是干涉支那內政","createTime":"2020-07-28T05:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T08:43:14.000Z","uid":83713,"like":117,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"3d69b3a763ffd66088733a466487aa91152ebb88","tid":2128640,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:50:02.000Z","msg":"紐西蘭宣布暫停執行與香港的引渡協議，並改變對香港出口敏感商品的政策，所有軍事、軍民兩用物品及技術出口，將採取與中國內地同樣的措施。當局又更新旅遊建議，提醒國民在香港可能觸犯港區國安法的風險。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">中國駐紐西蘭使館發言人對此表示強烈不滿和堅決反對，批評有關決定嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則，粗暴干涉中國內政，又說任何對華施壓的圖謀都絕不會得逞，敦促紐西蘭立即改弦更張，停止以任何方式干涉香港事務和中國內政，以免對兩國關係造成進一步損害。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540314-20200728.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540314-20200728.htm&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=395e1cc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540314-20200728.htm&h=2ef79dc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540314-20200728.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n明明係紐西蘭內政，變左支那內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d524660c4a62e3003942b6a87f8f89d39b7b2a5","tid":2128640,"uid":248290,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:52:02.000Z","msg":"世界都是 支那的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf406fdf28c49e6a022528af60731e886e9429a6","tid":2128640,"uid":5499,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"好悶，日日都係呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d193020bd4bea1d16d6e94ab23dc2d60f58fe160","tid":2128640,"uid":127575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img